Leaders of All Progressives Congress (APC) in Ibadan South East Local Government of Oyo South have supported the senatorial ambition of Adegboyega Adegoke They pledged their support when Adegoke visited them at the home of Alhaji Muftau Gbayau. Party Chairman in Oyo South Alhaji Mojeed Olaoya said there must not be any ploy to circumvent the popular rule by imposition or consensus.   Sanwo-Olu, Fashola for Traffic Radio’s colloquium     APC youths seek 35 per cent inclusion in govt     Petroleum body fires Ondo task force chair   The leaders based their support for Adegoke on his development projects in Oyo State. Gbayau, who spoke for the others, said they will  ensure Adegoke wins the primaries. He appealed to members, leaders and delegates to support Adegoke’s aspiration for better representation.